title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data in a table inside a grid cell
OB: When attempting to export data in a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown
EB: The export of data from a table inside a grid cell should not result in an exception being thrown
SR:
To reproduce this issue, follow these steps:
1. Insert a grid
2. Insert a table into one of the grid cells
3. Insert another table into another grid cell
